			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Yes if the mob bashes and hits there is a chance your song will be stopped.
<br />

<br />
And yes there is no channeling skill for bards.
<br />

<br />
However even if we did have channeling that will not help against bash/stun interrupts. Because if you ask a caster they will tell you that channeling doesn't help with stun type attacks, it helps with fizzle and regular interrupts such as moving or being attacked. You could be confused with Channeling AA that helps with fizzles.
<br />

<br />
There is only 1 way for stun type attacks to be recovered.
<br />

<br />
And its Persistant Casting AA.
<br />

<br />

<br />
(Correct me if I am wrong, not sure if there is a item that helps with stun type interrupts.)</span></td>
